9 5. IN THE CASE OF CANCELLATION PERFORMED IN
10 PERSON, BE PERFORMED IN A MANNER SIMILAR TO THE IN–PERSON METHOD THE
11 CONSUMER USED TO CONSENT TO THE AUTOMATIC RENEWAL, WHICH MAY INCLUDE
